{"tid":1655284,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"聯合國人權專家訪港","createTime":"2019-10-15T03:47:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T06:50:19.000Z","uid":334008,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"c24d4b06c8936e503a18e04b9c62fcf98d620c0d","tid":1655284,"uid":334008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T03:47:13.000Z","msg":"11月9至11日聯合國以下人權專家訪港，想親身同佢地討論香港人權狀況既請報名:<br />\n- Dr Fernand de Varennes, Special Rapporteur on minority issues<br />\n- Ms Pia Oberoi, Senior Advisor on Migration and Human Rights for the Asia Pacific region, based in the Bangkok office of the Office of the United Nations High Commissioner for Human Rights<br />\n<br />\n同場仲有Dr Surya Deva, Member, United Nations Working Group on Business and Human Rights (佢本身都base喺香港)<br />\nMs Leilani Farha, Special Rapporteur on adequate housing會錄片講香港房屋問題<br />\n英國學者同大律師Jason Pobjoy會講難民兒童權利<br />\n<br />\n成個event既日程：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/events/913488878985825/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fevents%2F913488878985825%2F&d=P9V%2Fg5HR%2BYIczjwvlITT9FNDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=b83d5ea1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/events/913488878985825/</a><br />\n報名呢度：<a href=\"https://forms.gle/Z1ijAYrKHEA41QbG8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FZ1ijAYrKHEA41QbG8&d=P9V%2Fg5HR%2BYIczjwvlITT9FNDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=96fa657d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/Z1ijAYrKHEA41QbG8</a> 　<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 感謝<br />\n<br />\n(如果想知多啲Special Rapporteurs既工作，請睇<a href=\"https://www.ohchr.org/EN/HRBodies/SP/Pages/Welcomepage.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ohchr.org%2FEN%2FHRBodies%2FSP%2FPages%2FWelcomepage.aspx&d=P9V%2Fg5HR%2BYIczjwvlITT9FNDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=008754d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ohchr.org/EN/HRBodies/SP/Pages/Welcomepage.aspx</a>)"},{"p